Organics:
 
She smiled and shook Silence's hand.
 
"Have you met my brothers yet?  I'm sure you have met one of them at least."

Dark Mouse <raccoon7679@...> wrote:
Silence::

She had sworn to keep the peace.  She got up and offered her hand to
Organics. "Hello. Pleased to meet you."


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
